max_freqs = [384182.5]*15
#max_freqs=[384178.599, 384179.091, 384184.733]
zipped_data = list(zip(dfs, max_freqs))
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for i, (df, max_freq)  in enumerate(zipped_data[:]):
    data = df.dropna()
    freqs = ((max_freq-PUMP_FREQUENCY)-(data['tempV']-data['tempV'].min())*FREQVSVOLT- (data['currV']-data['currV'].min())*FREQVSCURR)
    ax=plot_spline_fit(ax, x=freqs, y=data['ratio'], yerr=data['ratioErr'],scolor=f'C{i}', mfc=f'C{i}',color=f'C{i}', s=0.0, ms=5, figsize=(10, 10), label=fr"$\delta$ = { 180-2*df.iloc[10]['pump_AOM_freq'] :.2f}", linewidth=2.5)

plt.legend()

plt.savefig(os.path.join(MEASURE_FOLDER, 'lossFeatures.png'))

max_freqs = [384182.5]*15
#max_freqs=[384178.599, 384179.091, 384184.733]
zipped_data = list(zip(dfs, max_freqs))
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for i, (df, max_freq)  in enumerate(zipped_data[:]):
    data = df.dropna()
    if (180-2*df.iloc[10]['pump_AOM_freq']==8):
        continue
    freqs = ((max_freq-PUMP_FREQUENCY)-(data['tempV']-data['tempV'].min())*FREQVSVOLT- (data['currV']-data['currV'].min())*FREQVSCURR)
    ax=plot_spline_fit(ax, x=freqs, y=data['ratio'], yerr=data['ratioErr'],scolor=f'C{i}', mfc=f'C{i}',color=f'C{i}', s=0.0, ms=5, figsize=(10, 10), label=fr"$\delta$ = { 180-2*df.iloc[10]['pump_AOM_freq'] :.2f}", linewidth=2.5)

plt.legend()

plt.savefig(os.path.join(MEASURE_FOLDER, 'lossFeatures.png'))
